{"tid":815422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印尼小男孩把玩巨蟒 網民負評：想送死？","createTime":"2018-09-12T05:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T09:37:41.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"01fd318aec365713df59de2d14afa7e1561b32d1","tid":815422,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:02:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IXq8PdSKXRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIXq8PdSKXRE&d=3rJsxH%2F%2B72fQ8TF%2FSjX6MozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4124aaf7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IXq8PdSKXRE</a><br />\n<br />\n時常聽見蛇可吞象，近日網上有一段影片，片中一名小男孩正在把玩一條巨蟒蛇，一時抓牠頭，一時騎著牠，有網民質疑拍片者是小男孩的父母，並齊聲譴責：「如果那條蛇很餓，你的孩子早就死定。」<br />\n<br />\n據外媒報道，估計短片拍攝地點為印尼，該名小男孩不知危險，把玩巨蟒蛇，又沒有人阻止他。有網民質疑拍片者如果是其父母，認真不負責任，尤如將兒子「送入蛇口」，想送死？影片上傳3日，吸引逾12萬點擊率，男孩完全沒有意識到危險。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/815041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F815041&d=3rJsxH%2F%2B72fQ8TF%2FSjX6MozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=97002f7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F815041&h=18c9a035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/815041</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到個標題仲以為係玩啲蛇仔<br />\n一睇條片 咁撚大條<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc998a24949bd3d6b0f7eea6baf144129ce8a078","tid":815422,"uid":109983,"like":0,"dislike":26,"score":-26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"其實唔難....<br />\n我下面都有條巨蟒"},{"pid":"a109eef77a2070a434d84104c811fcf9cf54f2c4","tid":815422,"uid":42469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T05:22:26.000Z","msg":"緬甸蟒個性溫馴，可以做寵物"},{"pid":"35e63583ddd9a82b32abcfdbea5a